        "timestamp": "2019-05-21 09:45:36.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI found quickfix for this.\n\nEdit: roles/dns/handlers/main.yml\n\nAnd add one more option to the dnsmasq (--dns-loop-detect):\ncommand: -H /simulated_hosts --log-facility=- --dns-loop-detect\n\nIt worked for me",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
